 class="t m0 x9 h17 yad ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">上千万之巨。<span class="_ _8"></span>堪布曾随晋美彭措法王远赴欧美、<span class="_ _8"></span>东南亚等多</div><div class="t m0 x9 h17 yae ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">国弘法，<span class="_ _6"></span>如今还通过现代的网络技术，<span class="_ _6"></span>广传大乘精髓，<span class="_ _6"></span>为芸</div><div class="t m0 x9 h17 yaf ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">芸众生普降法雨。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h17 yb0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 lsc ws0">在讲经说法之余，堪布<span class="_ _1a"> </span>2007<span class="_ _1a"> </span>年发起“启动爱心”的倡</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
